Realty One Group At the Beach Newport
DOMINION COAST AND VALLEY REAL ESTATE LLC

data.description:
Nestled in the sought-after gated community of Seagrove, this spacious 2,367 square foot home is truly special. It features three roomy bedrooms, all with generous walk-in closets, and two adaptable bonus rooms that can cater to your diverse needs.
Sitting on half an acre of land, the property provides ample space for all your aspirations.
The primary bathroom is a blank canvas, just waiting for your personal touch. Here's your chance to create a warm and luxurious spa-inspired atmosphere that reflects your unique style and preferences. But the real charm of this property extends beyond the front door - a large deck that's perfect for year-round outdoor fun. It's perched above your very own enchanting forested yard, ideal for hosting gatherings, enjoying local wildlife, or simply savoring the peace of nature.
The modest HOA fees make it easy to access a variety of amenities, including a swimming pool, a welcoming clubhouse with a billiard table, a well-maintained tennis and pickleball court, and secured RV/Boat storage. Seagrove offers a warm and welcoming atmosphere, and this home is your key to experiencing its unique charm.
